            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
              <span class="text-moxie-pink">MOXIE</span> is <span id="typewriter-text" class="text-charcoal" aria-live="polite"></span><span class="cursor text-moxie-pink">|</span>
            </h1>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 leading-relaxed text-gray-700 max-w-3xl">
            When women lead, the world is a safer and more equitable place for everyone.
            I help leaders transform courage, grit, and authenticity into lasting impact.
          </p>

